=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2532103\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2532103\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 08, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104spf1665703007836.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/spf1665703007836.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/spf1665703007836.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"spf1665703007836\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $format\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"spf1665703007836___format_266519\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return the field data, formatted according to the display format (DIS).\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"spf1665703007836__topic_d83816e1_d83817e1_d83818e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"spf1665703007836__p_d83819e1_d83820e1_d83821e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$format</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"spf1665703007836__p_d83822e1_d83823e1_d83824e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$format</span> = <var class=\"keyword varname\">FormattedData</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"spf1665703007836__topic_d55432e1_d55433e1_d55434e1_d55435e1_d55436e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d422648e75\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"spf1665703007836__p_d83828e1_d83829e1_d83830e1\">Field data, formatted according to the display format (DIS) of the field.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"spf1665703007836__topic_d55437e1_d55438e1_d55439e1_d55440e1_d55441e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d422648e84\">\n                       \n Use\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"spf1665703007836__p_d83834e1_d83835e1_d83836e1\">Allowed in the trigger formatToDisplay and formatFromDisplay or components.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"spf1665703007836__topic_d55442e1_d55443e1_d55444e1_d55445e1_d55446e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d422648e93\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"spf1665703007836__p_d83840e1_d83841e1_d83842e1\">You can use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$format</span> to change formatted data using the <var class=\"keyword varname\">FormattedData</var> argument.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"spf1665703007836__p_d83843e1_d83844e1_d83845e1\">Use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$format</span> only in the field-level formatToDisplay and formatFromDisplay triggers. When the formatToDisplay trigger is activated, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$format</span> initially returns the field data, formatted according to the display (DIS) template of the field. If a display template is not defined for the field, the default formats shown in the following table are used:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"spf1665703007836__table_d8666e1_d8667e1_d8668e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Default Display Templates Used by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$format</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"spf1665703007836__table_d8666e1_d8667e1_d8668e1__entry__1\">\n Data type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"spf1665703007836__table_d8666e1_d8667e1_d8668e1__entry__2\">\n Displayed format\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"spf1665703007836__table_d8666e1_d8667e1_d8668e1__entry__1\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"spf1665703007836__table_d8666e1_d8667e1_d8668e1__entry__2\">\n As is\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"spf1665703007836__table_d8666e1_d8667e1_d8668e1__entry__1\">\n Numeric\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"spf1665703007836__table_d8666e1_d8667e1_d8668e1__entry__2\">{<code class=\"ph codeph\">-</code>}<var class=\"keyword varname\">nnn</var>{<code class=\"ph codeph\">.</code>} </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"spf1665703007836__table_d8666e1_d8667e1_d8668e1__entry__1\">\n Float\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"spf1665703007836__table_d8666e1_d8667e1_d8668e1__entry__2\">{<code class=\"ph codeph\">-</code>}<var class=\"keyword varname\">nnn</var>{<code class=\"ph codeph\">.</code>}<code class=\"ph codeph\">e</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">nnn</var>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"spf1665703007836__table_d8666e1_d8667e1_d8668e1__entry__1\">\n Date, Linear Date\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"spf1665703007836__table_d8666e1_d8667e1_d8668e1__entry__2\">\n                        ccyymmdd\n                     </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"spf1665703007836__table_d8666e1_d8667e1_d8668e1__entry__1\">\n Time, Linear Time\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"spf1665703007836__table_d8666e1_d8667e1_d8668e1__entry__2\">\n                        hhnnsstt\n                     </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"spf1665703007836__table_d8666e1_d8667e1_d8668e1__entry__1\">\n Datetime, Linear Datetime\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"spf1665703007836__table_d8666e1_d8667e1_d8668e1__entry__2\">\n                        ccyymmddhhnnsstt\n                     </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"spf1665703007836__table_d8666e1_d8667e1_d8668e1__entry__1\">\n Boolean\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"spf1665703007836__table_d8666e1_d8667e1_d8668e1__entry__2\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">T</code> or <code class=\"ph codeph\">F</code>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"spf1665703007836__table_d8666e1_d8667e1_d8668e1__entry__1\">\n Image, Raw\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"spf1665703007836__table_d8666e1_d8667e1_d8668e1__entry__2\">\n TRX-coded data\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"spf1665703007836__p_d83846e1_d83847e1_d83848e1\">When the formatFromDisplay trigger is activated, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$format</span> initially returns the raw data for the field, as entered by the user. ProcScript in the formatFromDisplay trigger should convert this raw data into a format acceptable by Uniface. The converted data should be written to <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$format</span> when the formatFromDisplay trigger completes.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"spf1665703007836__p_d83849e1_d83850e1_d83851e1\">In the Debugger, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$format</span> can be accessed directly or as variable <code class=\"ph codeph\">$103</code>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"spf1665703007836__section_uk1_gpz_zbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d422648e271\">Example: Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$format</span></h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following example adds a sterling symbol in front of a number if\n               the currency is British:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"spf1665703007836__pre_gpq_gpz_zbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">; trigger: Format\nif (CURRENCY = \"POUNDSTG\")\n $format = \"STG %%$format\"\nendif\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/deb1665702681553.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>trigger formatFromDisplay</a><p>System trigger that temporarily converts the format of data in a field from an external format into an internal format, and makes that reformatted data available for processing purposes.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xzb1705583342348.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Drag-and-Drop Formats</a><p>Drag-and-drop formats are global objects that define drag and drop behavior, including the default action, pop-up menu, and icon that are available when performing drag and drop actions in the tree and picture widgets. They are not used for drag-and-drop widgets.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jok1665703129463.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>trigger formatToDisplay</a><p>System trigger that temporarily converts the format of data in a field from an internal format into an external format that is displayed or printed.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532103\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532103\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$format Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 08, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $format Return the field data, formatted according to the display format (DIS). $format $format = FormattedData Return Values Field data, formatted according to the display format (DIS) of the field. Use Allowed in the trigger formatToDisplay and formatFromDisplay or components. Description You can use $format to change formatted data using the FormattedData argument. Use $format only in the field-level formatToDisplay and formatFromDisplay triggers. When the formatToDisplay trigger is activated, $format initially returns the field data, formatted according to the display (DIS) template of the field. If a display template is not defined for the field, the default formats shown in the following table are used: Table 1. Default Display Templates Used by $format Data type Displayed format String As is Numeric { - } nnn { . } Float { - } nnn { . } e nnn Date, Linear Date ccyymmdd Time, Linear Time hhnnsstt Datetime, Linear Datetime ccyymmddhhnnsstt Boolean T or F Image, Raw TRX-coded data When the formatFromDisplay trigger is activated, $format initially returns the raw data for the field, as entered by the user. ProcScript in the formatFromDisplay trigger should convert this raw data into a format acceptable by Uniface. The converted data should be written to $format when the formatFromDisplay trigger completes. In the Debugger, $format can be accessed directly or as variable $103 . Example: Using $format The following example adds a sterling symbol in front of a number if the currency is British: ; trigger: Format if (CURRENCY = \"POUNDSTG\") $format = \"STG %%$format\" endif Copy Related Links trigger formatFromDisplay System trigger that temporarily converts the format of data in a field from an external format into an internal format, and makes that reformatted data available for processing purposes. Drag-and-Drop Formats Drag-and-drop formats are global objects that define drag and drop behavior, including the default action, pop-up menu, and icon that are available when performing drag and drop actions in the tree and picture widgets. They are not used for drag-and-drop widgets. trigger formatToDisplay System trigger that temporarily converts the format of data in a field from an internal format into an external format that is displayed or printed. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}